40|$|We {{present a}} method to verify the {{correctness}} of parallel programs that perform complex numerical computations, including computations involving floating-point arithmetic. The method requires that a sequential version of the program be provided, {{to serve as the}} specification for <b>the</b> parallel <b>one.</b> <b>The</b> key <b>idea</b> <b>is</b> to use model checking, together with symbolic computation, to establish the equivalence of the two programs. 1...|$|R
